"The current surface is _deliberately minimal_ — just enough to port the "
"simplest stdlib wrappers (`dotenv`, `nanoid`, `uuid`, `slugify`). It will "
"grow as real wrappers demand it; we'd rather under-design and add than "
"commit to a helper we later regret."
