#: src/native-libraries/manifest-v1.md:363
msgid ""
"For Apple app-bundle targets, Metal shader sources are compiled into "
"`default.metallib`. Set `PERRY_XCRUN=/path/to/fake-or-real-xcrun` to "
"override tool discovery in tests. Vulkan shader sources are compiled with "
"`glslc` into `NativeLibraries/<package>/vulkan/<source>.spv`; set "
"`PERRY_GLSLC=/path/to/glslc` to override discovery. D3D12 shader sources are"
" compiled with `dxc` into `NativeLibraries/<package>/d3d12/<source>.dxil`; "
"set `PERRY_DXC=/path/to/dxc` to override discovery. If your shader build "
"needs custom profiles, entry points, or flags, ship prebuilt `shaderOutputs`"
