#: src/platforms/ios.md:65
msgid "iOS apps use `UIApplicationMain` with a deferred creation pattern:"
msgstr "แอป iOS ใช้ `UIApplicationMain` ร่วมกับรูปแบบการสร้างแบบ deferred:"

#: src/platforms/ios.md:67
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"import { App, Text, VStack } from \"perry/ui\"\n"
"\n"
"App({\n"
"    title: \"My iOS App\",\n"
"    width: 400,\n"
"    height: 800,\n"
"    body: VStack(16, [\n"
"        Text(\"Hello, iPhone!\"),\n"
"    ]),\n"
"})\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/platforms/ios.md:80
msgid ""
"The `App()` call triggers `UIApplicationMain`, and your render function is "
"called via `PerryAppDelegate` once the app is ready."
msgstr ""
"การเรียก `App()` จะ trigger `UIApplicationMain` และฟังก์ชัน render "
"ของคุณจะถูกเรียกผ่าน `PerryAppDelegate` เมื่อแอปพร้อม"

