#: src/stdlib/http.md:326
msgid "AWS S3 / S3-Compatible Object Storage"
msgstr "AWS S3 / ที่เก็บอ็อบเจกต์ที่เข้ากันได้กับ S3"

#: src/stdlib/http.md:328
msgid ""
"[`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-"
"client`](https://github.com/bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client) is a zero-"
"dependency, MIT-licensed S3 client (~1.9k LoC, derived from the official "
"MinIO JS client without the lodash/async/xml2js baggage). It compiles "
"natively under `perry.compilePackages` with no patches required — verified "
"against a SigV4 presigned-URL byte-for-byte match with `bun` (issue #551)."
msgstr ""
"[`@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-"
"client`](https://github.com/bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client) เป็น S3 "
"ไคลเอนต์ที่ไม่มี dependency, มีลิขสิทธิ์ MIT (~1.9k LoC ดัดแปลงมาจาก MinIO "
"JS ไคลเอนต์อย่างเป็นทางการโดยไม่มี lodash/async/xml2js ติดมา) "
"คอมไพล์เนทีฟภายใต้ `perry.compilePackages` โดยไม่ต้องแพตช์ใดๆ — "
"ตรวจสอบแล้วว่า SigV4 presigned-URL ตรงกันแบบ byte-for-byte กับ `bun` (issue "
"#551)"

#: src/stdlib/http.md:333
msgid "\"@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client\""
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/http.md:338
msgid ""
"```typescript,no-test\n"
"import { S3Client } from \"@bradenmacdonald/s3-lite-client\"\n"
"\n"
"const s3 = new S3Client({\n"
"    endPoint: \"https://s3.us-east-1.amazonaws.com\",\n"
"    region: \"us-east-1\",\n"
"    bucket: \"my-bucket\",\n"
"    accessKey: process.env.AWS_ACCESS_KEY_ID,\n"
"    secretKey: process.env.AWS_SECRET_ACCESS_KEY,\n"
"})\n"
"\n"
"// Presigned GET URL (no network I/O — pure SigV4 signing)\n"
"const url = await s3.presignedGetObject(\"path/to/object.png\", { expirySeconds: 3600 })\n"
"console.log(url)\n"
"\n"
"// Upload bytes\n"
"await s3.putObject(\"path/to/object.txt\", \"hello world\", {\n"
"    metadata: { \"x-amz-acl\": \"public-read\" },\n"
"})\n"
"\n"
"// Stream a download — returns a standard fetch Response\n"
"const res = await s3.getObject(\"path/to/object.txt\")\n"
"console.log(await res.text())\n"
"\n"
"// Head / Delete / List\n"
"const meta = await s3.statObject(\"path/to/object.txt\")\n"
"console.log(meta.size, meta.lastModified)\n"
"\n"
"for await (const obj of s3.listObjects({ prefix: \"path/to/\" })) {\n"
"    console.log(obj.key, obj.size)\n"
"}\n"
"\n"
"await s3.deleteObject(\"path/to/object.txt\")\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/stdlib/http.md:373
msgid ""
"Same code works against any S3-compatible service — only `endPoint` changes:"
msgstr ""
