#: src/container/security.md:107
msgid ""
"Runs `cosign verify --certificate-identity ${CHAINGUARD_IDENTITY} "
"--certificate-oidc-issuer ${CHAINGUARD_ISSUER} <ref>@<digest>` and caches "
"pass/fail."
msgstr ""
"รัน `cosign verify --certificate-identity ${CHAINGUARD_IDENTITY} "
"--certificate-oidc-issuer ${CHAINGUARD_ISSUER} <ref>@<digest>` และ cache "
"ผลลัพธ์ pass/fail"

