msgid ""
"On fail, the FFI rejects with a `verification failed` error (the container "
"is never created)."
msgstr ""
"หากล้มเหลว FFI จะ reject พร้อม error `verification failed` (container "
"จะไม่ถูกสร้างขึ้น)"

